00:33:03.210 --> 00:33:09.400
open-mindedness, accessibility
and discoverability of data

00:33:09.400 --> 00:33:14.490
and knowledge exchange across such
a wide variety of disciplines.

00:33:14.490 --> 00:33:18.970
In our team, we have
paracytologists, medievalists,

00:33:18.970 --> 00:33:24.420 position:56%
historians, climate historians,
